{"id":678556,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/678556.html","date":"2022-03-23T04:39:21Z","modified":"2022-03-23T04:39:21Z","title":"听风言事｜新华社记者的英语没学好","content":"<p>作者：我是启风</p>\n<p>昨天，新华社发了一篇文章《<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4NDI3NjcyNA==&amp;mid=2649775055&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1a1fc66b1c5710247141ab11920f9e83&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\">又一夜过去，乌克兰局势有这些最新消息！</a>》，里边有这么一段：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/post-678556-623aa47d0a8b8.\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p>后来有人找到原文，发现里边写的是：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/post-678556-623aa47f46246.\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p>今天晚些时候，新华社自行编辑了文稿：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/post-678556-623aa481a5dba.\" alt=\"cdtimg\" /></p>\n<p>写这篇文章的几位作者一方面可能是英语不好，另一方面对当下俄乌局势似乎也缺少必要的了解。</p>\n","author":1067,"categories":[18271,43134,41492,38912,41420],"tags":[23753,45124,10040,10702]}